The paper discusses the use of citation relations among journals, which is a common topic in the fields of digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the potential for assessing interdisciplinarity, which could fall under the categories of social and information networks (cs.SI), software engineering (cs.SD), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
